      • getOptions

        public static List<Option> getOptions(Collection<?> items,
                                      String valueGetterName,
                                      String textGetterName)
        Shortcut method to return list of options for view given collection of objects. Value field is currently limited to primitive int type. Text field is currently limited to String type.
        Parameters:
        items - items to create list of options for
        valueGetterName - getter method name for the value (int type)
        textGetterName - getter method name for the text (String type)
        Returns:
        list of options for the items

      • getOptions

        public static <E extends Enum<E>> List<Option> getOptions(Class<E> enumType)
        Shortcut method to return list of options for the given enum class type. Enum name will be used for value, and toString() will be used for text.
        Parameters:
        enumType - enum class
        Returns:
        list of options for enum class

      • getOptions

        public static List<Option> getOptions(Collection<String> strings)
        Shortcut method to return list of options for the given collection of strings. Each String will be used for both the value and text of it's returned option.
        Parameters:
        strings - strings to create options for
        Returns:
        options for the strings
